    <item>
      <title>突尼斯选举季开始，总统竞争对手被捕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/tunisia-election-season-begins-with-president-s-rivals-arrested</link>
      <description><![CDATA[突尼斯选举季伊始，该国针对总统凯斯·赛义德的竞争对手和批评者展开了一系列逮捕行动，人们担心这场几乎没有竞争的选举结果将给这个曾经是阿拉伯世界最进步的民主国家造成沉重打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/tunisia-election-season-begins-with-president-s-rivals-arrested</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 16:22:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及维持创纪录高利率以抑制通胀放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/egypt-holds-record-high-rate-to-keep-lid-on-slowing-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及连续第二次会议将利率维持在历史最高水平，以确保在货币大幅贬值后通胀继续放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/egypt-holds-record-high-rate-to-keep-lid-on-slowing-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 16:19:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克押注特朗普为特斯拉提供保护，为 SpaceX 带来收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/musk-s-trump-wager-sets-up-shield-for-tesla-gains-for-spacex</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党候选人誓言要扭转拜登的电动汽车政策，但特朗普议程的其他方面将使他的亿万富翁恩人受益。]]></description>
