      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 16:00:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非反对派议员重启土地征用计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/south-african-opposition-lawmakers-revive-land-expropriation-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非主要反对党计划重启修宪尝试，允许无补偿征收土地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/south-african-opposition-lawmakers-revive-land-expropriation-bid</guid>
